{"tid":2302961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老母買咗樽消毒火酒，但一打開係酸酸地味，係咪中伏","createTime":"2020-11-27T13:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T14:17:05.000Z","uid":187009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f44b2ed377b485874b0bff940e9053715a50a75","tid":2302961,"uid":187009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"疫情關係，我地屋企會用火酒噴鞋底，之前用過幾樽2L火酒都有浸酒精味，但老母今次買嘅火酒就有D酸味， 噴落隻手揮發唔係快，我擔心佢比人呃，有冇巴打可以証實下，我試過燒過D火酒，係藍色帶小小紅，我地係咪中咗伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zRwoL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zRwoL0.jpg&h=60befbd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係呢個牌子，我上網咩都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b27ff3e5fbf2fe19303154bdca871c1d431b10c","tid":2302961,"uid":48901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"有機會係工業用，唔係醫療用<br />\n我公司工作都係需要用好多消毒酒精<br />\n三月果段時間都係買到一隻好酸嘅酒精<br />\n係韓國出品，不過係工業用途<br />\n唔知有無分別"},{"pid":"30a14f31127c4274c8b462e11ee8d2f3799fd25d","tid":2302961,"uid":17496,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"有酸味即係氧化曬變酸，可以倒曬佢"},{"pid":"d479d04ddc33fa8245def0b299ca9d843596112a","tid":2302961,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b27ff3e5fbf2fe19303154bdca871c1d431b10c","tid":2302961,"uid":48901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"有機會係工業用，唔係醫療用<br />\n我公司工作都係需要用好多消毒酒精<br />\n三月果段時間都係買到一隻好酸嘅酒精<br />\n係韓國出品，不過係工業用途<br />\n唔知有無分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"即係甲醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28d526f42d07552e7a6faa83dc6c5329e6bb2e2","tid":2302961,"uid":187009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a14f31127c4274c8b462e11ee8d2f3799fd25d","tid":2302961,"uid":17496,"li